      "description": "This folder groups the **admin/coach management and assessment-setup endpoints** for the local API (`http://localhost:8080`). It contains requests to:\n\n- **Authenticate** admins and coaches (login).\n    \n- **Provision core entities** such as **students**, **coaches**, and **subjects**.\n    \n- **Build and manage assessments**, including **creating tests**, **creating question sets**, and **assigning tests to students**.\n    \n- **Retrieve student evaluation metrics**, such as a student’s **SQI score**."
    },
